          <versionCode>00</versionCode>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Taxpayer Nondiscrimination and Protection Act of 2015</b></p> <p>Amends the federal criminal code to establish penalties for misconduct against a taxpayer by an Internal Revenue Service employee during the performance of official duties, specifically including a violation of the protections and guarantees afforded under the First Amendment of the Constitution to political speech and political expression.</p>]]></text>
